item.title: By: Christina
item.dc:creator: Christina
item.description:
Noah, you are a fine lawyer because you are a great man. I was so touched by your article about your family. With qualities like you have, success will follow. Be well, my friend.
Christina

item.title: By: Jamison
item.dc:creator: Jamison
item.description:
We miss Noah in D.C.
Terribly.
He is a great lawyer and an even better person.
But it sounds like the new practice is going great. Clients will be in good hands.
